                            <comment id="15290115" author="benlau" created="Wed, 18 May 2016 23:58:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=syuanjiang&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;syuanjiang&quot;&gt;Stephen Yuan Jiang&lt;/a&gt; I&apos;m not currently working on the hfile format revision.  The (to my knowledge) mostly complete/correct patch I included before in &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-14283&quot; title=&quot;Reverse scan doesn&#8217;t work with HFile inline index/bloom blocks&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-14283&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-14283&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; is what I have still.  I haven&apos;t had time to work on open source since then.  I may have time this quarter though to come back to the patch and fix conflicts/address any issues people raise.  Is this ticket blocking anything for you?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
